{"tid":1698113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"墨國毒梟殺美國摩門教家庭9死 特朗普揚言開戰","createTime":"2019-11-07T09:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T11:30:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"89278e856fe1ad74690ac5c57142a443af938379","tid":1698113,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"2019-11-06 星島日報<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1130044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1130044&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=711e4527\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1130044&h=f9fe3d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1130044</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191106/_2019110610315777513.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191106%2F_2019110610315777513.jpg&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=55f4bb83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191106%2F_2019110610315777513.jpg&h=9fa70628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191106/_2019110610315777513.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n受害的美國摩門教「勒巴倫」(LeBaron)家族（右），他們的汽車被燒得面目全非（左）。（網圖／AP )<br />\n<br />\n美國摩門教知名家族「勒巴倫」（LeBaron）的家族成員，周一在墨西哥北部索諾拉州開車前往婚禮途中遭槍手伏擊，至少九人遇害，包括三名女子和六個兒童，另有六名孩子受傷。死者均為美國籍，居於墨西哥北部。據說槍手是墨西哥販毒集團成員，當局指他們可能誤認遇襲者為敵對幫派成員。<span style=\"color: brown;\">美國總統特朗普得知後非常憤怒，在Twitter上揚言要清除這些「禽獸」，認為墨西哥的毒梟武裝達「軍隊」級別，願意派兵協助將其殲滅。墨西哥總統洛佩斯則認為不需要外國政府插手。</span><br />\n<br />\n兩個販毒集團的武力衝突導致美國人傷亡，當中不乏孩童。特朗普在社交網站表示，「現在是時候了，美國會幫助墨西哥向販毒集團宣戰，並將他們殲滅。我們就等你們偉大新總統的電話。」他說，「如果墨西哥清理這些禽獸需要幫助，美國隨時準備好伸出援手」、「毒梟集團已經如此龐大，有時需要用動用軍隊才能擊敗他們。」、「美國已經準備好，也願意介入，且能夠把事情處理得又快又好。」"},{"pid":"7a6c3100aabebfbd876e22f6e54eb45bbdda8de6","tid":1698113,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191106/_2019110610315777513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191106%2F_2019110610315777513.jpg&h=7d236a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2c0bc08d2b81aea8fe99afdb3be55ed6bd25182","tid":1698113,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"3323250a17015bd4322f917ac444910586c77b53","tid":1698113,"uid":277186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"要打一早打左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4a710bfd783eef9f823cf0fa3e23f32a44c154","tid":1698113,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"墨西哥總統個大佬就係毒梟，你叫佢點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e63e3e149780b4b8f2906f210e5a3270da20557","tid":1698113,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"摩門教點解係咁生"},{"pid":"e79ebe9d9da54fe28306a0c6745cee59db205d8d","tid":1698113,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e63e3e149780b4b8f2906f210e5a3270da20557","tid":1698113,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"摩門教點解係咁生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"好多美國鄉下佬都係咁生"},{"pid":"3f5dc6711d8109f64d6cd00f32801e12dd584292","tid":1698113,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e63e3e149780b4b8f2906f210e5a3270da20557","tid":1698113,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"